  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking an experienced and results-driven Sales Manager to lead the sales team in achieving targets, expanding client relationships, and driving sustained business growth.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead, manage, and motivate the sales team to consistently achieve monthly and yearly sales targets</li><li>Develop and implement strategic sales plans to increase revenue and market share</li><li>Build and maintain strong, long-term relationships with key clients and partners to enhance customer loyalty and retention</li><li>Identify and pursue new business opportunities to expand the customer base and drive growth</li><li>Oversee the entire sales cycle, including prospecting, negotiation, and closing, to maximize deal success</li><li>Monitor sales performance metrics and prepare accurate reports and forecasts to inform decision-making</li><li>Coach, train, and support sales team members to enhance their skills and improve overall sales effectiveness</li><li>Collaborate closely with internal teams to ensure seamless sales operations and customer satisfaction</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a Sales Manager or in a senior sales role demonstrating leadership and sales achievement</li><li>Strong leadership demonstrated by guiding teams to meet or exceed sales targets</li><li>Effective communication and negotiation skills applied to secure client agreements and partnerships</li><li>Target-driven mindset with demonstrated business and commercial acumen to identify growth opportunities</li><li>Ability to manage multiple priorities and client accounts efficiently</li><li>Self-motivated, proactive, and results-oriented approach to sales management</li><li>Capability to work independently and collaboratively within a team environment</li></ul>",
